他出版了许多著作，包括畅销小说《Il-Gaġġa》（“牢笼”），<ref>Aquilina, Sandra (12 March 2007). [http://www.independent.com.mt/news.asp?newsitemid=47723 "Portrait of the artist"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722222846/http://www.independent.com.mt/news.asp?newsitemid=47723 |date=2011-07-22 }}, ''The Malta Independent''. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref> 其作为1971年由Mario Philip Azzopardi导演的电影《Gaġġa》的蓝本，获得乐福门奖的《Samuraj》，<ref name="obit" /> 获得政府文学勋章的《Paceville》，<ref name="obit" /> 以及《Il-Holma Maltija》(“马耳他之梦”)，文学评论家Norbert Ellul-Vincenti<ref>Ellul Vincenti, Norbert (11 May 1994): "Vassalli's Maltese Dream", ''The Sunday Times'' (Malta), p. 20.</ref>对其写道“在马耳他文学中没有什么作品能与之媲美”。前总理及剧作家[[阿尔弗雷德·桑特|阿尔弗雷德·桑特]]<ref>Sant, Alfred (4 May 2001). [http://www.maltastar.com/pages/r1/ms10dart.asp?a=15283 "Frans Sammut: A Man of Courage"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.maltastar.com/pages/r1/ms10dart.asp?a=15283 |date=20120111094612 }}, ''maltastar.com''. Retrieved 15 May 2011.</ref> 认为森密的作品是“杰作”，英国作家和诗人Marjorie Boulton称之为“巨作”<ref>[http://www.independent.com.mt/news.asp?newsitemid=56739 Maltese works in Esperanto] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112121901/http://www.independent.com.mt/news.asp?newsitemid=56739 |date=2012-01-12 }}, ''The Malta Independent'', 2 September 2007. Retrieved 15 May 2001.</ref>。

==逝世==
Frans Sammut著名的遗言是：“我和妻子应该去耶路撒冷，然而似乎计划改变了。我现在要去天堂里的耶路撒冷了。”<ref>Sammut, Mark (15 May 2011). [http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20110515/social/Frans-Sammut.365455 "Frans Sammut"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20110515/social/Frans-Sammut.365455 |date=20170905094901 }}, ''The Sunday Times'' (Malta). Retrieved 25 May 2011.</ref>

